title: MisterMusic Show 309  new indie,alternative,rock Radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 309 [120 minutes] 192kbps MP3 stereo



New tunes on the show this week by Tennis and Craft Spells.

The oldie of the week spent 4 weeks at number 1 on the US modern rock chart 16 years ago in June 1998. One of the band's best known songs.
Plus the usual mix of over 5 decades of rock, indie and alternative classics.




The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
